## PROJECT NOTES

*Edit this section per project. The examples below are for the Progress app — adapt for your project.*

**Typical files to audit:**
- `melodyScheduler.js` — pitch selection, clustering, foreshadowing, timing
- `professionalMelodyScheduler.js` — professional mode melody generation
- `mgen/src/orchestrator.js` — MGEN multi-pass generation
- `synthEngines.js` — envelope generation (ADSR)
- `synth.js` — tone playback, synthesis routing
- `melodyCountermelody.js` — counterpoint generation
- `melodyTuning.js` — pitch snapping, scale mapping

**Typical state properties to trace:**
- `state.melodyAdsr` — envelope sliders
- `state.synthParams.*` — per-synth parameters
- `context.proPhraseArch` — professional mode state
